name: Madness
description:
Madness from the Echo Fragments Collection, for #OBJKT4OBJKT.

In tribute to the Echo Fragments charity collection. Echo fragments is a collection of 1 of 1 NFTs (this one for OBJKTS4OBJKTS is an exception of 1000 mint) containing fragments of prose, lyrics, and poetry that resonate within our souls. They echo inside us. Some obvious, some not, they contain powerful notions that can break habits, change moods, and bring about change.

Read more about the collection and the charitable causes we support at: https://www.medium.com/@shackledart
